{"tid":873610,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有嚮香港文化中文音樂廳睇過節目既巴SIS打請入一入來, 位置問題..","createTime":"2018-10-23T14:26:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T16:29:09.000Z","uid":161049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9b7619cd2191f32432937fccf7f2b52142dd34c6","tid":873610,"uid":161049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T14:26:56.000Z","msg":"[url]<a href=\"https://ticket.urbtix.hk/internet/p_image/seat_plan/121482.jpg?t=1540304029230\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fticket.urbtix.hk%2Finternet%2Fp_image%2Fseat_plan%2F121482.jpg%3Ft%3D1540304029230&d=deIH71eHsYsDBVtARf2jYhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=23b3f244\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ticket.urbtix.hk/internet/p_image/seat_plan/121482.jpg?t=1540304029230</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n呢個係哈利波特seating plan<br />\n綠=480<br />\n粉=680<br />\n藍=980<br />\n黃=1080<br />\n<br />\n想請問一下點解平飛反而坐得前少少, 680同980又相差唔遠..<br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.lcsd.gov.hk/en/hkcc/common/images/facilities/concerthall/concert_hall_seating_plan_s.gif\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lcsd.gov.hk%2Fen%2Fhkcc%2Fcommon%2Fimages%2Ffacilities%2Fconcerthall%2Fconcert_hall_seating_plan_s.gif&d=deIH71eHsYsDBVtARf2jYhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=921a0251\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.lcsd.gov.hk/en/hkcc/common/images/facilities/concerthall/concert_hall_seating_plan_s.gif</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n同埋係咪右面會好過左面? 因為系統應該係會自動派最好位置,<br />\n入去買飛果時系統自動編 右面高層 F-L (J133, J134)既位比我<br />\n但係我自己睇番左面高層前第一排既E75, E76係仲有好多位,<br />\n會唔會左面係有D特別問題無咁好? 例如會窄少少, 因為見到輪椅位都係集中哂嚮左面"},{"pid":"8287d7f6fa5fb2d33d933e0c2d70193c107ea21a","tid":873610,"uid":161049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-23T14:30:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.lcsd.gov.hk/en/hkcc/common/images/facilities/concerthall/concert_hall_seating_plan_s.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lcsd.gov.hk%2Fen%2Fhkcc%2Fcommon%2